    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I prefer how the pager looked before #37905 with the pager's window height clamped to the height of the message window. Providing a method (either via a configuration option or a custom autocommand) would be appreciated.\n\nOriginally mentioned in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/37905#issuecomment-3923190726.",
