        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "This work well for me without flicker:\n```lua\napi.nvim_win_set_config = (function(orig)\n  return function(win, opts)\n    if opts.height and vim.bo[api.nvim_win_get_buf(win)].filetype == 'pager' then\n      opts.height = math.min(api.nvim_win_text_height(win, {}).all, math.ceil(vim.o.lines * 0.5))\n    end\n    return orig(win, opts)\n  end\nend)(api.nvim_win_set_config)\n```",
            "created_at": "2026-03-20T05:52:17Z",
